title: Post
description: More panos from the Sunset, Ocean Beach, and Stern Grove.
description_full:
More panos from the Sunset, Ocean Beach, and Stern Grove.

Some hits and some misses: overlapping exposures, missed focus (I suspect the film wasn‚Äôt always flat inside the camera), color shifts from expired film / old chems / guessed exposure.

But film is about the process as much as anything. Best I can do is trust it.
